  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599380256088-ONX42Y2ZO0PFO213GM1A/14a-evaliciouspuffy.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>One of my dear creative partners, <a href=\"http://evalicious.bigcartel.com/\">Evalicious</a>, sent a marvelous assortment of products to play with. I'm a big fan of puffy stickers in general, and these are no exception.</p><p>Since I am pressed for time these days, I managed to squeeze an hour of creative time in to create a one page Project Life type of spread. Love their acrylic stamp sets - I mean, how cute is that camera?</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"14b-20131121-035322.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599380303192-CSR511KSIXLUMRAYDG5D/14b-20131121-035322.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"14c-20131121-035334.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599380303613-Q0DB5OV2PMCKZKKUSCET/14c-20131121-035334.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"14d-20131121-035346.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599380304058-MIT4INHGWCXXNJMX4NGC/14d-20131121-035346.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The best part of waking up these days is our morning conversations with Jack. He is so cheery and doesn't make a fuss. Once fed, he either falls back asleep or stays up to talk (well, coo) up a storm. It's a special time to savor. The family photo was taken a couple days after the others, but I am not the least bit concerned. So glad I got this documented, and it may just be the way to go these days. I used my Project Life mini kit from Cut &amp; Paste and other supplies from Two Peas In A Bucket and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\">Simon Says Stamp</a>. Here is how the spread turned out:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599380342927-KTR9LUI8V1Y96BRH42N1/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://evalicious.bigcartel.com/\">Evalicious</a> is a small indie, online shop that offers scrapbooking paper tags, badge buttons and rubber stamps. They have just added <a href=\"http://evalicious.bigcartel.com/products?search=puffy+stickers&amp;search-submit=\">puffy stickers </a>to their line of products as well as new collection called <em>Everday </em>which features feminine yet masculine colors, has a focus on good eats with a touch of wood and chalkboard. Their products add just the right touch to your scrapbook layouts, PL spreads and paper projects.</p><p><strong>CONNECT WITH EVALICIOUS |</strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shopevalicious\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/shopevalicious\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"http://www.shopevalicious.com/\">Blog</a></p><p><strong>GIVEAWAY IS CLOSED, THANKS FOR ALL YOUR COMMENTS: $30 e-gift code. Check out </strong><a href=\"http://evalicious.bigcartel.com/\"><strong>the shop</strong></a><strong> and leave a comment here with your favorite item.</strong> Comments will close Saturday, Nov 23 at 8am PST and a winner will be announced shortly after. GOOD LUCK! WINNER IS: #98 - <a href=\"http://www.mgold16.blogspot.com/\">Melissa Antolovic</a> says: November 21, 2013 at 5:57 pm CONGRATS!</p><p><strong>REMEMBER, you can still take advantage of the special offer: 15% off all </strong><a href=\"http://evalicious.bigcartel.com/\"><strong>Evalicious</strong></a><strong> purchases using code: AMY15 (expires Nov 25).</strong></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
